                <msContents>
                  
                    <summary>Pustaha. Dairi-Batak. Pangulubalang, aggressive magic, but mostly the incantations (tabas) only. From Guru Dalihan Ni Aji to Tanda Ni Aji. The pupil is admonished, not to leave the book open so that other people may see the text, because his teacher has paid 88 [dollars] to his teacher for these instructions. At the end there are some Arabic prayers in Batak script.</summary>
                    
